#

Herb-Crusted Salmon with Savory Herb Mashed Potatoes

35 min
$15
650 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy Option

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main DishSide Dish

Tags:

Easy DinnerHealthyQuick Meal

Description

A deliciously easy dish combining tender salmon with a flavorful herb crust, paired with creamy mashed potatoes infused with herbs.

Ingredients

  • salmon fillets: 2 (6 oz each)
  • breadcrumbs: 1/2 cup
  • fresh parsley, chopped: 1/4 cup
  • fresh dill, chopped: 2 tbsp
  • olive oil: 3 tbsp
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • potatoes, peeled and cubed: 4 medium
  • butter: 2 tbsp
  • milk: 1/4 cup
  • chives, chopped: 2 tbsp
